hadiths[38]{hadithnumber,text}:
5640,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo museebat bhi kisi musalman ko pahunchti hai Allah Taala usey uske gunah ka kaffara kar deta hai (kisi musalman ke) aik kaantaa bhi agar jism ke kisi hisse mein chubh jaey.
5641,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalman jab bhi kisi pareshaanii, beemaarii, ranj w malaal, takleef aur gham mein mubtala ho jata hai yahan tak ke agar usey koi kaantaa bhi chubh jaey to Allah Taala usey uske gunahon ka kaffara bana deta hai."
5642,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke musalman jab bhi kisi pareshaanii, beemaarii, ranj w malaal, takleef aur gham mein mubtala ho jata hai yahan tak ke agar usey koi kaantaa bhi chubh jaey to Allah Taala usey uske gunahon ka kaffara bana deta hai."
5643,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke momin ki misal paudey ki sabse pehli nikli hui harii shaakh jaisi hai ke hawa usey kabhi jhukaa deti hai aur kabhi barabar kar deti hai aur munafiq ki misal Sanoobar ke darakht jaisi hai ke wo seedha hi khada rehta hai aur aakhir aik jhokey mein kabhi ukhad hi jata hai. aur Zakariya ne bayan kya ke ham se Sad ne bayan kya, unse ibne-Ka'b ne bayan kya, unse unke walid maajid mohtaram Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi bayan kya."
5644,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke momin ki misal paudey ki pehli nikli hui harii shaakh jaisi hai ke jab bhi hawa chaltii hai usey jhukaa deti hai phir wo seedha ho kar museebat bardasht karne mein kaamyaab ho jata hai aur badkaar ki misal sanoobar ke darakht jaisi hai ke sakht hota hai aur seedha khada rehta hai yahan tak ke Allah Taala jab chahta hai usey ukhaad kar phenk deta hai.
5645,"maine Saeed bin Yasar Abul-Hubaab se suna, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala jiske sath khair w bhalai karna chahta hai usey bimari ki takaaleef aur dusri museebaton mein mubtala kar deta hai."
5646,maine (wafaat k marz ki takleef) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada aur kisi mein nahi dekhi.
5647,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aap ke marz ke zamane mein hazir hua Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt badey tez bukhar mein they. maine arz kya : (ya rasoolullaah!) aapko bada tez bukhar hai. maine ye bhi kaha ke ye bukhar aapko isliye itna tez hai ke aap ka sawab bhi 2 guna hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, jo musalman kisi bhi takleef mein giraftaar hota hai to Allah Taala uski wjah se uske gunah is tarah jhaad deta hai jaisey darakht ke pattey jhad jatey hain."
5648,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aapko shadeed bukhar tha maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aapko bahut tez bukhar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, mujhey tanha aisa bukhar hota hai jitna tum mein ke 2 aadmiyon ko hota hai. maine arz kya ye isliye ke aap ka sawab bhi 2 guna hai? farmaya ke haan, yahi baat hai, musalman ko jo bhi takleef pahunchti hai kaatna ho ya us se zyada takleef dene wali koi cheez to jaisey darakht apne patton ko giraataa hai isi tarah Allah paak us takleef ko us ( musalman (ke gunahon ka kaffara bana deta hai."
5649,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bhookey ko khana khilaao aur mareez ki iyaadat yani mizaaj pursi karo aur qaidi ko chhudaao.
5650,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein saat (7) baton ka hukm diya tha aur saat (7) baton se mana farmaya tha. hamein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne soney ki anguthi , resham , deebaa , istibraq ( reshamii kapdey ( pahnney se aur qassi aur مثیرہ ( reshamii ( kapdon ki dusri qismein pahnney se mana farmaya tha aur aap ne hamein ye hukm diya tha ke ham janaaze ke peechhey chalein, mareez ki mizaaj pursi karein aur salam ko phailaaein."
5651,"main aik martaba bimar padaa to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) paidal meri iyaadat ko tashrif laey un buzurgon ne dekha ke mujh par be-hoshii ghalib hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur apne wuzu ka pani mujh par chhidkaa, us se mujhey hosh aa gaya to maine dekha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif rakhtey hain, maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! main apne maal mein kya karun kis tarah iska faisla karun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey koi jawab nahi diya. yahan tak ke meeraas ki aayat nazil hui."
5652,"mujh se Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, tumhen mein aik jannati aurat ko na dikhaa dun? maine arz kya ke zaroor dikhaaiin , kaha ke aik siyah aurat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aai aur kaha ke mujhey mirgii aati hai aur uski wjah se mera sattar (badan) khul jata hai. mere liye Allah Taala se dua kar dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar to chahey to sabr kar tujhey jannat milegii aur agar chahey to main terey liye Allah se is marz se nijat ki dua kar dun. us ne arz kya ke main sabr karoongii phir us ne arz kya ke mirgii ke waqt mera sattar khul jata hai. aap Allah Taala se uski dua kar dein ke sattar na khula kare. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske liye dua farmai."
5653,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala ka irshad hai ke jab main apne kisi bande ko uske 2 mahboob aaza (aankhon) ke barey mein aazmaata hun (yani naa-beenaa kar deta hun (aur wo is par sabr karta hai to iske badley mein usey jannat deta hun."
5654,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hijrat karke Madina tashrif laey to Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bukhar ho gaya. bayan kya ke phir main unke paas (iyaadat ke liye) gaee aur poochha, mohtaram walid aap ka mizaaj kaisa hai? Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi puchha ke aap ka kya haal hai? bayan kya ke jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bukhar hua to wo ye sher padha kartey they ''har shakhs apne ghar walon mein subah karta hai aur maut uske tasmey se bhi zyada qareeb hai.'' aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab fayda hota to ye sher padhtey they ''kaash mujhey malum hota ke kya phir aik raat wadi mein guzaar sakunga aur mere charon taraf izkhir aur Jaleel (Makka Mukarrama ki ghaas (ke jangal hongey aur kya main kabhi Mujanna (Makka se chand miil ke faasle par aik baazaar) ke pani par utroonga aur kya phir kabhi shaamma aur Tufail (Makka ke qareeb 2 pahaadon) ko main apne samney dekh sakoonga.'' Aaisha (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur aapko uski itlaa di Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai ke aey Allah ! hamarey dil mein Madina ki mohabbat bhi utni hi kar de jitni Makka ki mohabbat hai balke us se bhi zyada aur uski aab w hawa ko hamarey muwafiq kar de aur hamarey liye iske mudd aur saa mein barkat ata farma, Allah iska bukhar kahin aur jagah muntaqil kar de usey maqam Johfa mein bhej de."
5655,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik sahibzadi ( Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ( ne aapko kahlwaa bhejaa. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Sad (Raziallahu anhu) aur hamara khayal hai ke Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) they ke meri bachchii bistare-marg par padi hai is liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey yahan tashrif laaiin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein salam kahlwaayaa aur farmaya ke Allah Taala ko ikhtiyar hai jo chahey de aur jo chahey le-ley har cheez iske yahan mutaiyan w malum hai. isliye Allah se us museebat par ajr ki ummeedwaar raho aur sabr karo. sahibzadi ne phir dobara qism de kar aik aadmi bulaney ko bhejaa. chunanche aap khadey huey aur ham bhi aap ke sath khadey ho gaey phir bachchii Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki god mein utha kar rakhi gaee aur wo jaan nikalney ki haalat mein pareshan thi. aap ki aankhon mein aansu aa gaey. is par Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! ye kya hai? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye rehmat hai. Allah Taala apne bandon mein se jiske dil mein chahta hai rakhta hai aur Allah Taala bhi apne unhein bandon par raham karta hai jo khud bhi raham karne waley hotey hain.
5656,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik dehati ke paas uski iyaadat ke liye tashrif ley gaey. rawi ne bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi ki iyaadat ko tashrif ley jatey to mareez se farmatey ''koii fikr ki baat nahi. inshaAllah ye marz gunahon se paak karne wala hai'' lekin us dehati ne aap ke un Mubarak kalimaat ke jawab mein kaha ke aap kehtey hain ke ye paak karne wala hai hargiz nahi balke ye bukhar aik boodhey par ghalib aa gaya hai aur usey qabr tak pahuncha ke rahega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aisa hi hoga.
5657,aik Yahudi ladka Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat kya karta tha wo bimar hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski mizaaj pursi ke liye tashrif laey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Islam qabool kar ley chunanche us ne Islam qabool kar liya aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bayan kya apne walid se ke jab abu-Taalib ki wafat ka waqt qareeb hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas mizaaj pursi ke liye tashrif ley gaey.
5658,"kuchh sahaba Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aap ke aik marz ke doran mizaaj pursi karne aaey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein baith kar Namaz padhai lekin sahaba khadey ho kar hi Namaz padh rahe they. isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein baithney ka ishara kya. Namaz se farigh honey ke baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke imam isliye hai ke uski iqtida (pairvi) ki jaey to jab wo rukoo karey to tum bhi rukoo karo, jab wo sar uthaey to tum ( muqtadi ( bhi uthao aur agar wo baith kar Namaz padhey to tum bhi baith kar padho. abu-Adbullah imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke Humaidii ke mutabiq ye hadis mansukh hai kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aakhir (maut ke marz ( mein Namaz baith kar padhai aur log aap ke peechhey khadey ho kar iqtida (pairvi) kar rahe they."
5659,unke walid ( Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bayan kya ke main Makka mein bahut sakht bimar pad gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri mizaaj pursi ke liye tashrif laey. maine arz kya : aey Allah ke nabii! (agar wafat ho gaee to) main maal chhodunga aur mere paas siwa aik ladki ke aur koi waaris nahi hai. kya main apne 2 tehai maal ki wasiiyat kar dun aur aik tehai chhod dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi maine arz kya phir aadhey ki wasiiyat kar dun aur aadha (apni bachchii ke liye) chhod dun. farmaya ke nahi phir maine kaha ke aik tehai ki wasiiyat kar dun aur baqi 2 tehai ladki ke liye chhod dun? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik tehai kar do aur aik tehai bhi bahut hai. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath unki peshani par rakha (Sa'd (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya (aur mere chehrey aur pet par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna Mubarak hath phera phir farmaya : aey Allaah! Sad ko shifa ata farma aur uski hijrat ko mukammal kar. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath ki thandak apne jigar ke hisse par main ab tak pa raha hun.
5660,"Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapko bukhar aaya hua tha maine apne hath se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka jism chhuwa aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aapko to bada tez bukhar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, mujhey tum mein ke 2 aadmiyon ke barabar bukhar chadhtaa hai. maine arz kya ye isliye hoga ke aapko dugnaa ajr milta hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi bhi musalman ko marz ki takleef ya koi aur takleef hoti hai to Allah Taala uske gunahon ko is tarah giraataa hai jaisey darakht apne patton ko gira deta hai."
5661,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jab aap bimar they hazir hua. maine aap ka jism chhuwaa, aapko tez bukhar tha. maine arz kya aapko to bada tez bukhar hai ye isliye hoga ke aapko dugnaa sawab milega. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, aur kisi musalman ko bhi jab koi takleef pahunchti hai to iske gunah is tarah jhad jatey hain jaisey darakht ke pattey jhad jatey hain."
5662,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik shakhs ki iyaadat ke liye tashrif le gaey aur unse farmaya ke لا بأس طهور إن شاء الله''koii fikr nahi agar Allah ne chaha (ye marz ( gunahon se paak karne wala hoga'' lekin us ne ye jawab diya ke hargiz nahi ye to aisa bukhar hai jo aik boodhey par ghalib aa chuka hai aur usey qabr tak pahuncha kar hi rahega, is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir aisa hi hoga."
5663,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) gadhey ki paalaan par fidak ki chadar daal kar is par Sawar huey aur Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne peechhey sawar kya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ki iyaadat ko tashrif ley ja rahe they, ye jange-badr se pahley ka waqia hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rawaana huey aur aik majlis se guzrey jis mein Abdullah-bin-Ubai bin salool bhi tha. Abdullah abhi musalman nahi hua tha us majlis mein har giroh ke log they musalman bhi, mushrekeen bhi yani but parast aur Yahudi bhii. majlis mein Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, sawari ki gard jab majlis tak pahunchi to Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne apni chadar apni naak par rakh li aur kaha ke ham par gard na udaao. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein salam kya aur sawari rok kar wahan utar gaey phir aap ne unhein Allah ke taraf bulaya aur Quran Majeed padh kar sunaya. is par Abdullah-bin-Ubai ne kaha miyan tumhari baatein meri samajh mein nahi aatiin agar haq hain to hamari majlis mein unhein bayan karke ham ko takleef na pahunchaya karo, apne ghar jao wahan jo tumharey paas aaey us se bayan karo. is par ibne- Rawaha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kyon nahi ya Rasulullah ! aap hamari majlison mein zaroor tashrif laaein kyonke ham un baton ko pasand kartey hain. is par muslmaanon, mushrikon aur yahudiyon mein jhagdey bazi ho gaee aur qareeb tha ke aik doosrey par hamla kar baithtey lekin aap unhein khamosh kartey rahe yahan tak ke sab khamosh ho gaey phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni sawari par Sawar ho kar Sad-bin-Ubada (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif le gaey aur unse farmaya Sad ! tum ne suna nahi abu-Hubaab ne kya kaha, aap ka ishara Abdullah-bin-Ubai ki taraf tha. is par Sad (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke ya Rasulullah! usey maaf kar dijiye aur us se darguzar farmaiye. Allah Taala ne aapko wo nemat ata farma di jo ata farmaanii thi (aap ke Madina tashrif laney se pahley) is basti ke log is par muttafiq ho gaey they ke usey taaj pehna dein aur apna sardaar bana lin lekin jab Allah Taala ne us mansubey ko us haq ke zariey jo aapko us ne ata farmaya hai khatm kar diya to wo is par bigad gaya ye jo kuchh mamla us ne aap ke sath kya hai usi ka nateeja hai."
5664,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey aap na kisi khachchar par Sawar they na kisi ghodey par. ( balke aap paidal tashrif laey they).
5665,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere qareeb se guzrey aur main handi ke nichey aag sulgaa raha tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tumharey sar ki juwein tumhen takleef pahunchaatii hain. maine arz kya : ji haan! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hajjaam bulwaya aur us ne mera sar moond diya uske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey fidya ada kar dene ka hukm farmaayaa.
5666,"( sar ke shadeed dard ki wjah se) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : haaye rey sar ! is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar aisa meri zindagi mein ho gaya (yani tumhara intiqal ho gaya) to main tumharey liye istighfar aur dua karunga . Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha afsos , Allah ki qism ! mera khayal hai ke aap mera mar jana hi pasand kartey hain aur agar aisa ho gaya to aap to isi din raat apni kisi biwi ke yahan guzaarengey. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya balke mein khud darde-sar mein mubtala hun. mera irada hota tha ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke betey ko bula bhejoon aur unhein (khilaafat ki) wasiiyat kar dun. kahin aisa na ho ke mere baad kehney waley kuchh aur kahein (ke khilafat hamara haq hai) ya aarzoo karne waley kisi aur baat ki aarzoo karein (ke ham khaleefa ho jaaein) phir maine apne ji mein kaha (iskii zarurat hi kya hai) khud Allah Taala Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa aur kisi ko khaleefa na honey dega na musalman aur kisi ki khilafat hi qabool karengey."
5667,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapko bukhar aaya hua tha maine aap ka jism chhu kar arz kya ke aapko bada tez bukhar hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, tum mein ke 2 aadmiyon ke barabar hai. ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ajr bhi 2 guna hai. kaha haan phir aap ne farmaya ke kisi musalman ko bhi jab kisi marz ki takleef ya aur koi takleef pahunchti hai to Allah uske gunah ko is tarah jhaad deta hai jis tarah darakht apne patton ko jhaadtaa hai."
5668,"hamarey yahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laey main Hijjatul-wada ke zamane mein aik sakht bimari mein mubtala ho gaya tha maine arz kya ke meri bimari jis had ko pahunch chuki hai usey aap dekh rahe hain, main saahibe-daulat hun aur meri waaris meri sirf aik ladki ke siwa aur koi nahi, to kya main apna 2 tehai maal sadqa karun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi. maine arz kya phir aadha kar dun, aap ne farmaya ke nahi. maine arz kya aik tehai kar dun. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tehai bahut kafi hai agar tum apne waarison ko ghanii chhod kar jao ye us se behtar hai ke unhein mohtaaj chhodo aur wo logon ke samney hath phailaatey phirein aur tum jo bhi kharch karogey aur us se Allah ki khushnoodii hasil karna maqsud hoga is par bhi tumhen sawab milega. yahan tak ke us luqma par bhi tumhen sawab milega jo tum apni biwi ke munh mein daltey ho."
5669,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ka waqt qareeb aaya to ghar mein kai sahaba maujood they. umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi wahin maujood they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke lao main tumharey liye aik tahreer likh dun taake iske baad tum ghalat raah par na chalo. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt sakht takleef mein hain aur tumharey paas Quran Majeed to maujood hai hii, hamarey liye Allah ki kitab kafi hai. us mas'ale par ghar mein maujood sahaba ka ikhtilaf ho gaya aur bahas karne lagey. kuchh sahaba kehtey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (likhney ki cheezein ( de do taake Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisi tahreer likh dein jiske baad tum gumrah na ho sako aur kuchh sahaba wo kehtey they jo umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tha. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ikhtilaf aur bahas badh gaee to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke yahan se chaley jao. Ubaidullah ne bayan kya ke Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke sabse zyada afsos yahi hai ke unke ikhtilaf aur bahas ki wjah se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wo tahreer nahi likhi jo aap musalmanon ke liye likhnaa chahtey they."
5670,mujhey meri khala Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bachpan mein le gain aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah! mere bhaanjey ko dard hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere sar par hath phera aur mere liye barkat ki dua ki phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur maine aap ke wuzu ka pani piyaa aur maine aap ki peeth ke peechhey khadey ho kar nabwooat ki mehar aap ke donon kandhon ke darmyan dekhi. ye mohare-nubuwat hajla uroos ki ghundii jaisi thi.
5671,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kisi takleef mein agar koi shakhs mubtala ho to usey maut ki tamanna nahi karni chahiye aur agar koi maut ki tamanna karne hi lagey to ye kehna chaahiye ( اللهم أحيني ما كانت الحياة خيرا لي , Mina وتوفني إذا كانت الوفاة خيرا لي ( ''aey Allah ! jab tak zindagi mere liye behtar hai mujhey zinda rakh aur jab maut mere liye behtar ho to mujh ko utha ley.''"
5672,ham Khabbaab-bin-Arat (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan unki iyaadat ko gaey unhon-ne apne pet mein saat (7) dagh lagwaaey they phir unhon-ne kaha ke hamarey sathi jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein wafat pa chukey wo yahan se is haal mein rukhsat huey ke duniya unka ajr w sawab kuchh na ghataa saki aur unke amal mein koi kami nahi hui aur ham ne (maal w daulat ( itni paai ke jiske kharch karne ke liye ham ne mitti ke siwa aur koi mahal nahi paya (lagey Imaaratein banwaaney) aur agar Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein maut ki dua karne se mana na kiya hota to main uski dua karta phir ham unki khidmat mein dobara hazir huey to wo apni diwar bana rahe they unhon-ne kaha musalman ko har us cheez par sawab milta hai jisey wo kharch karta hai magar is (kam bakht) Imaarat mein kharch karne ka sawab nahi milta .
5673,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kisi shakhs ka amal usey jannat mein dakhil nahi kar sakega. sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ka bhi nahi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya nahi, mera bhi nahi, siwa iske ke Allah apne Fazal w rehmat se mujhey nawaazey isliye (amal mein) miyaanaa rawii ikhtiyar karo aur qareeb-qareeb chalo aur tum mein koi shakhs maut ki tamanna na karey kyonke ya wo nek hoga to ummeed hai ke uske aamaal main aur izafa ho jaey aur agar wo bura hai to mumkin hai wo tauba hi kare."
5674,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mera sahara liye huey they (marzul-maut mein) aur farma rahe they ( اللهم اغفر لي وارحمني وألحقني بالرفيق الأعلى ( ''aey Allaah! meri maghfirat farma mujh par raham kar aur mujh ko achchhey rafeeqon (farishton aur paighambaron) ke sath mila de. ''"
5675,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi mareez ke paas tashrif ley jatey ya koi mareez aap ke paas laya jata to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua farmaatey أذهب الباس رب Naas ، Mina padhi. اشف وأنت الشافي لا شفاء إلا شفاؤك ، Mina padhi. شفاء لا يغادر سقما ''aey parwardigar logon ke ! bimari door kar de, aey insanon ke paalne waley ! shifa ata farma, to hi shifa dene wala hai. teri shifa ke siwa aur koi shifa nahi, aisi shifa de jis mein marz bilkul baqi na rahe.'' aur Amr bin abi Qais aur Ibrahim bin tahmaan ne Mansoor se bayan kya, unhon-ne Ibrahim aur abu zuhaa se ke ''jab koi mareez Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas laya jata. ''"
5676,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey main bimar tha Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wuzu kya aur wuzu ka pani mujh par daala ya farmaya ke is par ye pani daal do, us se mujhey hosh aa gaya. maine arz kya ke main to kalaala hun (jiske walid aur aulad na ho) mere tarke mein taqseem kaisey hogi is par meeraas ki aayat nazil hui."
5677,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hijrat karke Madina tashrif laey to Abu-Bakar aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko bukhar ho gaya. bayan kya ke phir main unke paas ( beemar pursi ke liye) gaee aur puchha ke mohtaram waalid! aap ka kya haal hai aur aey Bilal ! aap ka kya haal hai? bayan kya ke jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko bukhar hota to wo ye sher padha kartey they. ''har shakhs apne ghar walon mein subah karta hai aur maut iske tasmey se bhi zyada qareeb hai''aur Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ka jab bukhar utartaa to buland awaz se wo ye ashaar padhtey. ''kaash mujhey malum hota ke main aik raat wadi (Makka) mein is tarah guzaar sakunga ke mere charon taraf izkhir aur Jaleel ( ghaas (ke darakht hongey aur kya kabhi phir main Mujanna ke ghaat par utar sakunga aur kya kabhi shaamma aur Tufail main apne samney dekh sakoonga.'' rawi ne bayan kya ke Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha phir main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq kaha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dua farmaaii اللهم حبب إلينا المدينة كحبنا مكة أو أشد وصححها وبارك لنا في صاعها ومدها وانقل حماها فاجعلها بالجحفة''aey Allah ! hamarey dilon mein Madina ki mohabbat paida kar jaisa ke hamein (apne watan ( Makka ki mohabbat thi balke us se bhi zyada Madina ki mohabbat ata kar aur uski aab w hawa ko sihat bakhsh bana de aur hamarey liye iske saa aur mudd mein barkat ata farma aur uske bukhar ko kahin aur jagah muntaqil kar de usey Johfa ( naam ke gaaun ( mein bhej de. ''
